Dialogue: 1,0:00:09.11,0:00:10.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗  孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:10.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, kids?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.53,0:00:12.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.53,0:00:12.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:12.36,0:00:13.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:13.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.82,0:00:15.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:15.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.74,0:00:21.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁住在深海的大菠萝里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:21.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who lives in a pineapple under the sea?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.00,0:00:22.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:22.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.79,0:00:24.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方方黄黄伸缩自如
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:24.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Absorbent and yellow and porous is he
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.96,0:00:26.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:26.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.79,0:00:29.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果四处探险是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:29.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If nautical nonsense be something you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.00,0:00:30.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:30.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.76,0:00:33.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就敲敲甲板让大鱼开路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:33.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then drop on the deck and flop like a fish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.09,0:00:34.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:34.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
