Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.00,0:01:11.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:11.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There we go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.09,0:01:12.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(856,376)}德克萨斯
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.52,0:01:14.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我把树叶都扫成一堆了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.52,0:01:14.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Spongebob, I got all the leaves raked--
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  这边怎么还有树叶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob, what are all these leaves doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.92,0:01:21.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不是要扫起来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.92,0:01:21.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You said you were gonna rake 'em?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.88,0:01:23.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在扫了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.88,0:01:23.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am raking the leaves
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.39,0:01:25.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可地上还是到处都有树叶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:25.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But they're still all over the ground
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.35,0:01:27.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  我最多就只能扫这么快了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.35,0:01:27.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, I can't rake any faster
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.33,0:01:28.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些可是大树叶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.33,0:01:28.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These are big leaves
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.32,0:01:33.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还会没完没了裂成不少小树叶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:33.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And they keep breaking in to more leaves
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.65,0:01:36.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事干就去给盐砖抛光什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.65,0:01:36.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then go scrape the salt lick or something
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.61,0:01:39.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,趁还来得及把事情都解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:39.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We gotta get this stuff done before it's too late
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.62,0:01:41.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这到底是在急什么  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:41.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the big rush anyway, Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.91,0:01:43.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都跟你说了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:43.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.72,0:01:45.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我下周冬眠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.72,0:01:45.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm hibernating next week
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.54,0:01:46.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冬眠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:46.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hibernating?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.97,0:01:47.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.97,0:01:47.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.75,0:01:49.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一整个冬天都要睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:49.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's when I go to sleep for the whole winter
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.85,0:01:50.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也会那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.85,0:01:50.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I do that?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.50,0:01:52.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会  傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:52.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, silly
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.86,0:01:54.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哺乳动物才会冬眠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.86,0:01:54.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a mammalian thing
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.33,0:01:58.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  你可能没注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.33,0:01:58.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, you may not have noticed
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.22,0:02:01.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我正是百分百的哺乳动物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:01.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I is 100% mammal
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.53,0:02:04.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别闲聊了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.53,0:02:04.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enough chitter-chatter, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.57,0:02:06.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,时间不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:06.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We don't have much time left
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.12,0:02:07.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:07.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.20,0:02:07.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:07.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When does your
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.94,0:02:09.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,渗碳作用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.94,0:02:09.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,carburation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.94,0:02:09.60,注释,,0,0,0,,[ carburation（渗碳作用）\N与 hibernation（冬眠）谐音 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.60,0:02:10.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啥时候开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:10.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,begin?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.72,0:02:12.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一周过后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.72,0:02:12.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In one week
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.15,0:02:14.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是珊迪  那样就只剩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:14.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But Sandy, that only gives us--
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.06,0:02:15.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一二三
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.06,0:02:15.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,one, two, three--
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.80,0:02:18.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,168个小时可以一起玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:18.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,168 more hours of play time--
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.72,0:02:19.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:19.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're telling me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.97,0:02:21.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有不少事没做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:21.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And there's still so much to do
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.46,0:02:23.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要去攀岩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.46,0:02:23.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We gotta climb some things
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.62,0:02:24.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,攀岩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:24.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Climb
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.28,0:02:26.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要去蹦极
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.28,0:02:26.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We gotta jump off of stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.25,0:02:26.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蹦极
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:26.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jump
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.90,0:02:28.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要去骑行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.90,0:02:28.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We gotta ride
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.50,0:02:29.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,骑行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:29.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ride
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.15,0:02:31.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还不想睡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.15,0:02:31.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go to sleep yet
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.14,0:02:31.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.14,0:02:31.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.85,0:02:34.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我睡觉期间可燃烧不了体内的碳水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.85,0:02:34.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't burn carbs in my sleep
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.75,0:02:35.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:35.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.15,0:02:36.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:36.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.13,0:02:37.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  我愿意为你献出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:37.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, I'm willing to sacrifice
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.90,0:02:41.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还没出卖给蟹老板的任何时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:38.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,any of my time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:41.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that I haven't already sold to Mr. Krabs to you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.35,0:02:43.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就好  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:43.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm glad, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.25,0:02:44.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为之后这七天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:44.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because for the seven days
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.72,0:02:46.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只有你我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:46.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's going to be you, me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.90,0:02:48.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有这俩吸汗头带在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:48.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and these sweat bands
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:52.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(782,732)}沙山
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.45,0:03:14.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以解释
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:14.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can explain
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.51,0:03:21.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我热血沸腾得不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:21.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm hotter than a hickory smoked sausage
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.19,0:03:35.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许要是我们唱了歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:35.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe, if we sing that song
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.55,0:03:36.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它就能活过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:36.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he'll come to life
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.90,0:03:37.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:37.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.69,0:03:40.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从前有个沙人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:40.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, there once was a sand man--
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.30,0:03:46.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生活想怎么极限就怎么极限
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:46.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Life's as extreme as you want to make it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.79,0:03:49.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许我们唱错了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:49.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe we didn't sing it right
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.42,0:03:54.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:54.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.84,0:03:58.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好大的运动量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:03:58.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a workout
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.09,0:03:59.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我明天一定还会有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:03:59.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be feeling this tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.88,0:04:03.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真是太出彩了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:03.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta say I'm impressed with you, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.69,0:04:07.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冬眠预备周有你在就是好得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.69,0:04:07.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're making this the best pre-hibernation week ever
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.35,0:04:10.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得先回家了  免得小蜗又咬烂沙发
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:08.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd better get home
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:10.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before Gary chews up the sofa again
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.55,0:04:25.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:25.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goodnight, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.05,0:04:45.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一大早清爽游个泳最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:45.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing like a refreshing morning dip
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.95,0:04:47.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:47.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,huh, Spongebob?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.69,0:04:49.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,睡一半干嘛要起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.69,0:04:49.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened to sleeping?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.56,0:04:51.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一整个冬天都要睡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:51.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be asleep all winter
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.03,0:04:54.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只剩三天时间可以玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:54.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we only got three days for fun
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.00,0:04:55.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:04:55.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, hurry now
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.12,0:04:57.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巨蚌就喜欢在这种时候进食
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:04:57.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The giant clams like to feed at this hour
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.06,0:05:08.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:08.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't this great?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.69,0:05:12.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实  从没玩过这么极限的捡针游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.69,0:05:12.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I've never played extreme jacks before
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.69,0:05:12.56,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 捡针游戏：抛一颗球\N在球落地前捡起尽可能多的针 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.31,0:05:14.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:14.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.63,0:05:16.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这次一定特有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:16.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this one's gonna be fun
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.02,0:05:19.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱俩拿着巨型挖耳棒对打
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.02,0:05:19.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We just whack each other with these giant ear cleaners
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.21,0:05:20.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁掉下去谁就输
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:20.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,till one of us falls off
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.95,0:05:23.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各就各位  预备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:23.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On your mark, get set--
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.62,0:05:25.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  你确定应该要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:25.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, are you sure we're supposed
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.79,0:05:26.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,站在这上面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.79,0:05:26.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to be standing up here?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.93,0:05:27.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:27.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:32.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1042,952)}海底针
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.52,0:05:34.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:34.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.70,0:05:36.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们去工园骑双人自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:36.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going for a tandem ride through the park
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.96,0:05:38.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一听就很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:38.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, that sounds safe--
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.62,0:05:39.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.62,0:05:39.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, fun
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.42,0:05:45.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行  我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:45.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.20,0:05:52.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是说好要去公园骑车吗  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought you said
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:52.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we were riding through the park, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.27,0:05:53.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:53.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去工业园
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The industrial park
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.71,0:05:57.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真本事就得在这使
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.71,0:05:57.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is where the real action is
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.59,0:05:59.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,踏板使劲踩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:05:59.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, pedal
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这段特别要技术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This part gets pretty technical
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.00,0:06:04.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,骑到高速跑道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:04.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now for the speed course
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.55,0:06:05.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,撑着点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:05.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hang on
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.85,0:06:08.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望能成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:08.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope we make it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.30,0:06:16.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我玩得也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:16.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm having fun too
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.82,0:06:26.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快醒醒  慢乌龟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:26.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wake up, slowpoke
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.76,0:06:28.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要去空中钓鱼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:28.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going fly fishing
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.24,0:06:32.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这只松鼠想杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:32.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This squirrel's trying to kill me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.25,0:06:33.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再玩这种危险动作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:33.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Any more of these stunts
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.45,0:06:34.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就要化为一滩死水了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:34.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'll be reduced to a puddle
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.03,0:06:39.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下  一定要想办法找借口脱身
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:39.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, I gotta talk my way out of this
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.25,0:06:41.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  我得跟你说个事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:41.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, I think I need to tell you something
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.04,0:06:41.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:41.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.72,0:06:43.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只是我感觉有点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.72,0:06:43.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just that I'm feeling sort of--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.07,0:06:47.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我感觉很需要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:47.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just feel like maybe I need to--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.34,0:06:49.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你先等着  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:49.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold that thought, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.87,0:06:52.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在来整点我在南方乡下老家的最爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:52.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,cause it's time for a down-home favourite
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.66,0:06:54.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进针堆找干草
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:54.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,find the hay in the needle stack
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.72,0:07:06.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:06.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you find it?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.02,0:07:08.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还没
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:08.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not yet
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.12,0:07:09.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就到这边找
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:09.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going to look over here
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.62,0:07:11.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.62,0:07:11.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You do that
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.28,0:07:15.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:15.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Found it, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.08,0:07:17.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来  三局两胜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:17.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, best two out of three
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.13,0:07:19.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.13,0:07:19.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotta hide
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.07,0:07:20.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:20.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotta hide
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.92,0:07:21.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,家里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:21.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Home?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.65,0:07:23.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  小蜗会说漏嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.65,0:07:23.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Gary can't keep a secret
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.23,0:07:25.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,石头底下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:25.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Under a rock
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.61,0:07:27.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太有创意了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:27.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's so original
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.42,0:07:30.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:30.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.49,0:07:35.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.49,0:07:35.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.18,0:07:38.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在哪  小方块
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:38.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are you, little square dude?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.81,0:07:40.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝的领带
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:40.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob's tie
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.27,0:07:42.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有他身上其他衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:42.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and all his other little dressings
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.67,0:07:43.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:43.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.40,0:07:45.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可他都会先叠好衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:45.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But he always folds his clothes
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.50,0:07:49.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后才会到处裸奔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:49.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before running around in the nude
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.08,0:07:51.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他一定是出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:51.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something terrible must've happened to him
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:54.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(410,356)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.24,0:07:58.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们大家都听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:58.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, listen up, y'all
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.15,0:08:00.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就此召集搜索队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:08:00.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm rounding up a search party
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.17,0:08:01.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:01.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob's gone missing
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.07,0:08:04.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救生艇就位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:04.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Man the lifeboats
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.63,0:08:06.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,阿尔法小队  搜索住宅区
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:06.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alpha team, you search uptown
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.67,0:08:08.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黄金小队  搜索市中心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:08.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gold team searches downtown
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.30,0:08:09.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家谁有异议
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:09.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Any questions?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.26,0:08:11.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黄金小队最强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:11.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gold team rules
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.02,0:08:13.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:13.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now get moving
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.67,0:08:16.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:16.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:16.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(652,244)}寻人启事
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.25,0:08:18.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来人找那边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:18.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Someone look up there
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.89,0:08:20.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都给我卖力点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:20.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put your dorsal fins into it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.82,0:08:26.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加把劲  他有可能就在硫磺泉某处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:26.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, he can be anywhere in these sulphur fields
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.22,0:08:28.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:28.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.47,0:08:35.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码我气质还在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.47,0:08:35.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, at least I still have my personality
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.28,0:08:37.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到潮湿洞穴里面找
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:37.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check in this here moist cave
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.41,0:08:40.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:40.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.21,0:08:44.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,报告情况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:44.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Status report
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.37,0:08:47.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他不在毒海胆湾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:47.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's not in the poison sea urchin cove
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.60,0:08:48.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再去找
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:48.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, look again
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.95,0:08:51.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他不在水蛭养殖场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.95,0:08:51.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's not at the leech farm
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.28,0:08:52.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再去找
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:52.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, look again
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.92,0:08:54.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他不在我脑海里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:54.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's not in my thoughts
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.95,0:08:56.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再去想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:56.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, think again
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.62,0:08:59.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全裤头村请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:59.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention, Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.68,0:09:01.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在必须双倍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:01.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the time has come to double
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  三倍努力去找
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no, triple our efforts
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.90,0:09:05.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:05.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about a break?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.27,0:09:06.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都已经找好几天了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:06.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've been at it for days
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.52,0:09:09.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,考虑一下小朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:09.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Think about the children
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.69,0:09:11.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:11.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a good idea
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.10,0:09:14.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让小朋友爬进一般人进不去的小地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:13.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Use the children to crawl into small places
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:14.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you couldn't normally reach
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.90,0:09:18.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全是一派胡言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:18.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a load of barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都听见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I heard that
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.22,0:09:22.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没找到海绵宝宝  谁都不准走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.22,0:09:22.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one's going anywhere till we find Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.78,0:09:23.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.78,0:09:23.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.77,0:09:24.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在这
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:24.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,here he is
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That ain't Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.22,0:09:27.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝是方的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.22,0:09:27.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob is square
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.87,0:09:31.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了  我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:31.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready, I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.88,0:09:33.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:33.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, you ain't
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.01,0:09:34.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到方块宝宝了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:34.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I found Squarebob
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:34.34,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1092,422)}海草哥
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.34,0:09:35.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那只是个麦片盒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:35.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's just a cereal box
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.77,0:09:37.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且他是黄的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:37.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Besides, he's yellow
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.38,0:09:38.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就在这
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:38.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, here he is
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.62,0:09:40.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:40.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could I go home now
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.00,0:09:42.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看  他就在天上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:42.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, look, he's up in the sky
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.23,0:09:45.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他没
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:45.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's not--
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.42,0:09:49.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们一定再去找了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:49.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They must've gone to search some more
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.70,0:09:55.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:55.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob, where are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.20,0:09:57.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在下面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:57.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You under there?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.41,0:10:00.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:00.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.85,0:10:04.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以解释
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:04.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can explain
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.52,0:10:05.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:05.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.12,0:10:07.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:07.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.24,0:10:08.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:08.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.92,0:10:10.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:10.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.11,0:10:13.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:13.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob, where are you?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:14.60,0:10:15.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 2,0:10:14.60,0:10:15.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 3,0:10:15.88,0:10:16.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 2,0:10:15.88,0:10:16.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.63,0:10:19.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那只松鼠疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:19.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That squirrel's gone crazy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.17,0:10:21.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但她一定不会去找石头底下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.17,0:10:21.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But she'll never look under a rock
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.98,0:10:22.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:22.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You said it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.97,0:10:24.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪找不到我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:24.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy'll never find us
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.86,0:10:31.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  你们不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:31.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, you don't understand
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.61,0:10:34.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看  是我海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:34.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, look, it is I, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.49,0:10:35.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在空地上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:35.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,out here in the open
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.02,0:10:37.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:37.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.97,0:10:40.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托  放我进去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:40.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, let me back in
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.67,0:10:41.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.67,0:10:41.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't understand
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.45,0:10:45.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我都担心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:45.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Spongebob, I was so worried
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.82,0:10:48.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还以为你出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.82,0:10:48.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought something terrible happened
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.17,0:10:49.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.17,0:10:49.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.30,0:10:51.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有时间可以去粉碎原子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:51.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's just enough time to go atom smashing
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.71,0:10:53.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:53.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.04,0:10:54.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没空再等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:54.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no time to wait
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.80,0:10:57.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要冬眠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:57.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hibernation
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.09,0:10:59.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  一定要抽空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:10:59.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, you gotta make time
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.23,0:11:00.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是大事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:11:00.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is important
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.45,0:11:05.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是男子汉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:05.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am a man
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.30,0:11:07.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:07.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.34,0:11:07.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.34,0:11:07.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I--
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.93,0:11:08.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:08.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I--
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.80,0:11:11.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没法再跟你玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:11.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't play with you anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.30,0:11:14.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我受不了你玩的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:14.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just can't take the games
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.14,0:11:17.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都快把我撕碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:17.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're tearing me apart
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.43,0:11:21.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我全坦白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:21.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There I said it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.19,0:11:24.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,答应我继续当朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.19,0:11:24.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, just promise we can still be friends
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.42,0:11:26.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.42,0:11:26.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.38,0:11:27.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这真的很难开口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:27.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this isn't easy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.62,0:11:28.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:28.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I--
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.75,0:11:35.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:35.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.51,0:11:40.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从来没想过会说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:40.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd say it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.05,0:11:42.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢海神王她冬眠了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:42.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but thank Neptune for hibernation
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.85,0:11:52.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们都是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:52.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:56.86,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(357,346)}罪犯生活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:11:59.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(260,408)\frz19}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:12:01.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:11:59.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19\pos(412,716)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:01.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(414,338)\frz24.04}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:04.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz22.06\pos(300,378)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:04.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(488,704)\frz24.13}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:04.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:08.66,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(458,438)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.56,0:12:08.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在回到甲壳类犯罪剧场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.56,0:12:08.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now back to the Crustacean Crime Theatre
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.51,0:12:15.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,站住  小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:15.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop, thief
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.36,0:12:16.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他往哪跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:16.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Which way did he go?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.30,0:12:17.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往那跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:17.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He went that way
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.60,0:12:18.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:18.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get him boys
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.87,0:12:24.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该死  又失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.87,0:12:24.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Curses, foiled again
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.84,0:12:28.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那家伙实在太坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:28.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a no good eel in the kelp that guy was
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.37,0:12:30.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小偷就是最坏的坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:30.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There ain't nothing worse than a thief
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.52,0:12:32.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就该把小偷关一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:32.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thieves need to be locked up forever
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.60,0:12:34.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把鳃都吊起来  绞死他们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:34.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They should all be strung up by their gills
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.82,0:12:36.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,强迫他们呼吸空气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:36.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and forced to breathe air
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.48,0:12:39.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可蟹老板  那你偷的东西怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:39.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Mr. Krabs, what about all the stuff you stole?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.85,0:12:40.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:40.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.61,0:12:41.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比如说那个桶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:41.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like that barrel
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:43.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(524,400)}咸海农场所有
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.78,0:12:44.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上面写  咸海农场所有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:44.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It says property of Salty Sea Farms
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.90,0:12:46.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我腌椰菜都是到那租的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:46.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's where I rent me pickles from
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.74,0:12:48.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来桶也是租来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:48.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you renting the barrel too?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.20,0:12:49.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个  不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:49.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, no
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.91,0:12:51.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就是你买的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:51.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then you bought it?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.00,0:12:51.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:51.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.83,0:12:53.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那样不就是偷了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:53.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then isn't that stealing?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.54,0:12:54.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个  我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:54.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I, uh--
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.87,0:12:57.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那这条热泉桑拿的毛巾怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:57.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about this towel from the Sizzling Spring Sauna?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:57.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(394,606)}热泉桑拿
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.00,0:12:58.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:12:58.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's--
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.46,0:13:00.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有比基尼贝尔电话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:13:00.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And this Bikini Bell phone?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.05,0:13:00.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个  我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:00.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.71,0:13:02.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有珊迪的灌木剪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:02.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And Sandy's hedge clippers?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.40,0:13:02.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.40,0:13:02.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're um--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.67,0:13:04.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有痞老板的割草机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:04.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And Plankton's lawnmower?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.01,0:13:04.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:04.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, he--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.68,0:13:06.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连泡芙老师的卷发器你都有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:06.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even Mrs Puff's hair curlers?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.50,0:13:07.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是人家送的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:07.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That one was a gift
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.77,0:13:11.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好了  那些都是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.77,0:13:11.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen, all that stuff is, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.77,0:13:12.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,借来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:12.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,borrowed
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.64,0:13:13.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,借来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:13.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Borrowed?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.60,0:13:14.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:14.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a relief
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还以为你没经过允许就拿了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought you took it without permission
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.15,0:13:18.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要什么允许啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:18.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Permission, shmermission
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.35,0:13:21.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,东西想什么时候借就什么时候借
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:21.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can borrow anything you want, anytime
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.30,0:13:24.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,趁人家没发现东西丢了  还回去就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:24.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as long as you get it back before it's missed
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.57,0:13:28.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,人尽皆知的事情  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:28.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone knows that, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.47,0:13:29.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:29.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.83,0:13:31.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:31.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, then
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.81,0:13:32.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱抱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:32.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hugs
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.50,0:13:35.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们今天干活可努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:35.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you put in a hard day's work, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.05,0:13:36.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我没在这上班
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.05,0:13:36.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I don't work here
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.12,0:13:37.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:37.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you later
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.56,0:13:39.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差点就露馅了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:39.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was close one
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.53,0:13:43.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你今天想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:43.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you want to do today?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.00,0:13:45.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你今天想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:45.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you want to do today?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.48,0:13:47.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道  你今天想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.48,0:13:47.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know, what do you want to do today?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.65,0:13:48.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.65,0:13:48.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.31,0:13:49.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你今天想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:49.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you want to do today?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.75,0:13:50.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:50.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.60,0:13:52.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你今天想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:52.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you want to do today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:54.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(974,890)}气球
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.34,0:13:56.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道今天想干什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.34,0:13:56.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know what I want to do today
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.55,0:14:00.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要来点钱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.55,0:14:00.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need some money
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.35,0:14:08.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:08.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't have any money
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.30,0:14:12.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我特别特别想要气球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:12.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob, I want a balloon really, really badly
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.04,0:14:16.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特别特别想要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:16.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really, really badly
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.88,0:14:18.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事的  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.88,0:14:18.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's OK, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.15,0:14:21.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝第一国家银行有不少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:19.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's lots of money
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:21.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the First National Bank of Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.81,0:14:24.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:24.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Follow me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.20,0:14:29.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也破产了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:29.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm broke too
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.51,0:14:32.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许可以找章鱼哥借钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:32.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe we can borrow money from Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.22,0:14:35.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  与其借钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:35.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, instead of borrowing the money
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.95,0:14:39.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不如就直接借气球好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:39.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,why don't we just borrow the balloon?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.19,0:14:40.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:40.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.15,0:14:41.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟蟹老板一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:41.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.86,0:14:43.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就单纯是借一下  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:43.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just borrowing, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.95,0:14:46.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  借一下不会有事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:46.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and borrowing is OK
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.23,0:14:48.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要能还回去就行  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:48.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as long as we bring it back, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.25,0:14:49.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:49.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.84,0:14:55.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,实在太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.84,0:14:55.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is so great
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.78,0:14:57.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定可以玩得特开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.78,0:14:57.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're gonna have so much fun
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.60,0:14:59.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以先拿着气球到处跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:59.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First, we can run with the balloon
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.37,0:15:01.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  然后可以拿着气球去海滩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:01.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, then we could go to the beach with the balloon
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.75,0:15:04.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  然后可以拿着气球骑自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:04.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, then we could take a bike ride with the balloon
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.78,0:15:05.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后能去看电影
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:05.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then we could go to the movies
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.70,0:15:06.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打电玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:06.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the arcade
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.35,0:15:06.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,溜个冰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.35,0:15:06.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the ice rink
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.92,0:15:07.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,买披萨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:07.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the pizza shop
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.67,0:15:08.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上月球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:08.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the moon
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.22,0:15:08.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:08.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the sky
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.84,0:15:10.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再上垃圾箱后边的车
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:10.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and then a car behind the dumpster
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.47,0:15:11.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再去糖果店
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:11.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the candy shop
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.38,0:15:12.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再去我后院
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:12.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then my backyard
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.17,0:15:13.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再上飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:13.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then in a plane
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.01,0:15:13.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爬石头顶上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:13.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And over a rock
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.76,0:15:14.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爬山底下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:14.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And under a hill
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.55,0:15:15.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,陪着大鲸鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:15.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And with a whale
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.52,0:15:17.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们喜欢借
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.52,0:15:17.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We love borrowing
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.15,0:15:23.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:23.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It popped
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.32,0:15:31.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在该怎么还回去  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:31.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How are we gonna return it now, Spongebob?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.57,0:15:32.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:32.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got the pieces
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.45,0:15:33.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:33.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got the air
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.57,0:15:34.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快  把碎片拼起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:34.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry, put the pieces on
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.89,0:15:38.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们让气球爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:38.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We popped the balloon
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.44,0:15:40.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还不回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:40.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can't return it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.36,0:15:42.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:42.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're thieves
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.05,0:15:45.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须去自首
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:45.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have to confess
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.78,0:15:46.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自首
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.78,0:15:46.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Confess?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.88,0:15:48.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你什么毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:48.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.54,0:15:51.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知不知道上面会怎么处置我们这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.54,0:15:51.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea what they do to people like us?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.25,0:15:53.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们这可不是搞什么诈骗邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.25,0:15:53.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're not talking about some dumb mail fraud scheme
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.73,0:15:55.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者是搞劫持
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.73,0:15:55.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or hijacking here
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.45,0:15:58.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们偷了个气球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:58.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we stole a balloon
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.70,0:16:00.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上面要把我们关起来一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:00.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And they're going lock us up forever
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.47,0:16:01.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:01.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.19,0:16:02.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保持头脑清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:02.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've just got to keep our heads
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.26,0:16:04.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,表现正常点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:04.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Act normal
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.32,0:16:15.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是卖艺的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:15.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Street performers
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.45,0:16:21.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:21.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not working
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:27.50,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(930,864)}气球
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.09,0:16:25.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:25.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, there
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.35,0:16:29.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要免费气球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:29.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you want a free balloon?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.92,0:16:31.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天是全国免费气球节
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:31.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's national free balloon day
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.38,0:16:34.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他发现我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:34.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's on to us
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.58,0:16:36.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村再也不安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:36.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not safe in Bikini Bottom anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.92,0:16:39.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动作一定要快  隐藏好行踪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:39.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've gotta move fast and cover our tracks
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.19,0:16:41.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就来  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:41.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm on it, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.17,0:16:50.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后再看一眼吧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.17,0:16:50.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take a last look, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.22,0:16:51.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.22,0:16:51.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can never go back
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.12,0:16:54.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:54.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.32,0:16:56.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们路途中只有彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:56.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've only got ourselves
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.11,0:16:58.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有背负的行囊和罪责
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:58.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and what we can carry on our backs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.24,0:16:58.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:16:58.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yup
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.28,0:17:04.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得轻装上阵才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.28,0:17:04.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're gonna have to travel lighter
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.90,0:17:12.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:12.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to go home
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.47,0:17:14.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,家回不了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.47,0:17:14.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can never go home, Pat
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.42,0:17:15.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是通缉犯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:15.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're wanted men
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.68,0:17:19.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,余生只能在四散奔逃中度过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:19.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll spend the rest of our lives running, running
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.55,0:17:21.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过起码坐在火边很暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:21.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But at least it's warm around the fire
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.70,0:17:24.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果是在海底  那怎么会有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,0:17:24.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If we're underwater, how can there be a--
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.45,0:17:28.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好怕  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.45,0:17:28.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm scared, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.44,0:17:30.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有暖呼呼的床
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:30.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more nice warm beds
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.19,0:17:32.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:32.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.57,0:17:35.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有邮件收得到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:35.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more getting mail
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.20,0:17:37.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:37.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.61,0:17:38.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有电影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:38.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more movies
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.51,0:17:40.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:40.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.78,0:17:42.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没珊迪  没珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:42.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more Sandy, or Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.95,0:17:44.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:44.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.50,0:17:47.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:47.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more anything
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.21,0:17:48.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:48.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want ice cream
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.75,0:17:53.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过处境也不算太难堪  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:53.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't have to be all bad, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.85,0:17:56.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码我们还有彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.85,0:17:56.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, at least we have each other
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.55,0:17:57.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:57.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.51,0:17:59.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且逃跑还能锻炼臀部还有大腿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:17:59.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And all that running is good for your buns and thighs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.95,0:18:00.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:00.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,right?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.67,0:18:02.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  臀部还有大腿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.67,0:18:02.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, buns and thighs
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还可以受冷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the bitter cold?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.25,0:18:05.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十分清爽宜人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:05.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's bracing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.98,0:18:09.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  当罪犯可能确实很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:09.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, maybe being a felon can be fun
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.12,0:18:11.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以解开领带
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:11.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can loosen our ties
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.99,0:18:12.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:12.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.30,0:18:15.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以自由飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:15.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And we could fly
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.87,0:18:16.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:16.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.42,0:18:24.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  飞不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:24.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, we still can't do that
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.54,0:18:26.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过也用不着刮毛了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:26.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we don't have to shave
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.22,0:18:28.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早就想到了  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:28.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm way ahead of you, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.79,0:18:31.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还可以讲话硬气点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:31.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you get to talk tough
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.17,0:18:35.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里一城不容我们二虎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:35.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This town ain't big enough for the two of us
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.71,0:18:36.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来试试
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:36.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me try
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.35,0:18:39.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,混账
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:39.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, punk
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.80,0:18:42.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最棒的一点就是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:42.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the best part is
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.27,0:18:43.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然我们是罪犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:43.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,now that we're felons
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.52,0:18:46.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,借到的东西就不用还回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:46.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we don't have to return anything we borrow
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.10,0:18:47.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:47.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.60,0:18:50.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后全都要怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:50.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And we owe it all to you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.56,0:18:52.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:52.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.45,0:18:54.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿气球的邪恶计划是你想出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.45,0:18:54.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Taking the balloon was your evil plan
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.28,0:18:57.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我光说不做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:57.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm nothing but a lot of talk
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.20,0:18:59.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真正下毒手的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:59.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're the one with the sticky fingers
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.12,0:19:03.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你这坏榜样最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:03.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you're the best bad influence ever
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.70,0:19:04.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:04.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You, too
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.82,0:19:10.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望有东西可以吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.82,0:19:10.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish we had something to eat though
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.07,0:19:13.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看我身上有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.07,0:19:13.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look what I've got
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.07,0:19:15.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,长方形
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.07,0:19:15.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rectangles
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.37,0:19:18.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可不是普通的长方形  是巧克力棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.37,0:19:18.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not just any rectangles, candy bars
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:18.34,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,218)}巧克力棒
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.90,0:19:23.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得把巧克力棒留着当后半辈子的干粮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.90,0:19:23.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All we have to do is make 'em last the rest of our lives
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.60,0:19:25.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:25.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.28,0:19:27.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在就吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:27.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I'll eat it now
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.81,0:19:35.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在就吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:35.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I'll eat it now
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.37,0:19:42.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我巧克力棒哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:42.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where'd my candy bar go?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.22,0:19:43.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定是丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.22,0:19:43.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must've dropped it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.95,0:19:45.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚吃了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:45.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just ate it, Pat
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.35,0:19:46.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃得满脸都是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:46.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all over your face
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.54,0:19:47.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:47.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where'd it go?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.69,0:19:48.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都快饿死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.69,0:19:48.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to starve
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.76,0:19:49.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.76,0:19:49.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where'd it go?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.04,0:19:54.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:54.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't find it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.47,0:19:55.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会在什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:55.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where could it possibly be?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.37,0:19:58.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咋了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.37,0:19:58.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.67,0:20:01.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你偷了我巧克力棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:01.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You stole my candy bar
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.87,0:20:02.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没偷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:02.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.60,0:20:05.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:05.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.18,0:20:08.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一朝当小偷  终生当小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:08.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Once a thief, always a thief
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.97,0:20:10.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你把你那条吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:10.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You ate yours
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.25,0:20:11.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这条是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:11.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is mine
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.60,0:20:14.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你把我唯一的干粮吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:14.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You took my only food
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.19,0:20:17.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我要挨饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.19,0:20:17.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I'm gonna starve
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.54,0:20:19.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.54,0:20:19.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.60,0:20:20.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我分我的一半给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.60,0:20:20.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just take half of mine
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.91,0:20:22.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.91,0:20:22.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yours?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.25,0:20:23.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说的是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:23.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean mine
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.97,0:20:25.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还要不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:25.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you want it or what?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.62,0:20:28.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除非你承认是你偷的  否则我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:28.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want it unless you admit you took it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.38,0:20:30.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是我的巧克力棒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:30.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is my candy bar
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.47,0:20:33.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,骗子骗子  我招枯梓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.47,0:20:33.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Liar, liar, plants for hire
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.55,0:20:35.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是火烧裤子  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.55,0:20:35.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's pants on fire, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.90,0:20:38.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你当然知道了  骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:38.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you would know, liar
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.55,0:20:40.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是你非要那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:40.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if you're gonna be that way
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就自个吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll eat it myself
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.57,0:20:43.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.57,0:20:43.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You better not
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.97,0:20:47.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我警告你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:47.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm warning you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.02,0:20:51.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:51.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.94,0:20:55.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:55.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.51,0:20:57.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.51,0:20:57.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.21,0:21:19.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就一神经病
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:19.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a crazy person
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.12,0:21:22.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自打你偷那气球  我就该料到了的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.12,0:21:20.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should've expected this
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:22.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,after the way you stole that balloon
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.67,0:21:23.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:23.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did I, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.80,0:21:24.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:24.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did I?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.62,0:21:27.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会不会是你的犯罪头脑催眠我去偷的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.62,0:21:27.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or did your criminal mind hypnotise me to steal it?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.82,0:21:30.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.82,0:21:30.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.12,0:21:34.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先是气球
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:34.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First, the balloon
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.50,0:21:35.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在又是我巧克力棒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:35.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, my candy bar
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.97,0:21:37.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.97,0:21:37.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're out of control
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.42,0:21:37.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.42,0:21:37.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.44,0:21:41.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要告发你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:41.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm telling on you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.40,0:21:43.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我先告发你再说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:43.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not if I tell on you first
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.65,0:21:45.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会比你先到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:45.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll beat you there
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.00,0:21:50.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就要有麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.00,0:21:50.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're gonna get in trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.70,0:21:53.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你才有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:53.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, you are
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:58.83,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(908,528)}警察局
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.57,0:22:07.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以为你们做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.57,0:22:07.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What can I do for you boys?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.35,0:22:11.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们偷了个气球
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.35,0:22:11.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We stole a balloon
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.70,0:22:16.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.70,0:22:16.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the problem here?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.84,0:22:18.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来是这两位偷了个气球
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.84,0:22:18.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it appears these two stole a balloon
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.90,0:22:20.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们会怎么处置我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.90,0:22:20.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do to us?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.97,0:22:25.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.97,0:22:25.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, follow me
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.00,0:22:29.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是坐不了牢  就别犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.00,0:22:29.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you can't do the time, don't do the crime
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.67,0:22:32.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  刑期满了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.67,0:22:32.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, time's up
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.35,0:22:34.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.35,0:22:34.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, get out
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.22,0:22:35.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:35.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But--
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.32,0:22:38.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我们偷了个气球
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.32,0:22:38.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but we stole a balloon
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.85,0:22:41.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  这天可是免费气球节
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:41.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, on free balloon day
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.34,0:22:49.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们路上要不要吃点棒棒糖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:22:49.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about some lollipops for the road, boys?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.72,0:22:53.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来发誓再也不会不经允许借东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:22:52.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's vow never to borrow anything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:53.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without permission again
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.80,0:22:55.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我同意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.80,0:22:55.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You said it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.39,0:23:02.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊  你们哪个警察偷了我棒棒糖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.39,0:23:02.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, which one of you flatfoots stole my lollipop?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.88,0:23:07.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可真是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.88,0:23:07.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, brother
Dialogue: 1,0:23:09.77,0:23:11.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.77,0:23:11.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean it
